name: Necklace Triskele Triple Spiral Wood Burned
description: Unique men's or ladies wooden necklace.Triple spiral(Druidism): Derived from the Greek word "Triskeles" meaning "three legs", the Triskele or Triple Spiral is a complex ancient Celtic symbol. Often referred to by many as a Triskelion, its earliest creation dates back to the Neolithic era, as it can be seen at the entrance of Newgrange, Ireland. The Triskele gained popularity in its use within the Celtic culture from 500BC onwards. This archaic symbol is one of the most convoluted to decipher as symbolists believe it is reflective of many areas of culture from the time.1)The motion of action, cycles, progress, revolution and competition.2)Life-death-rebirth, spirit-mind-body, mother-father-child, past-present-future, power-intellect-love and creation-preservation-destructionIt‚Äôs thought that through the combination of these two areas we gain one meaning of the Celtic triskele. It is believed to represent a tale of forward motion to reach understanding. However, this is thought not to be the only meaning, as it is also believed to represent three Celtic worlds; the spiritual world, the present world and the celestial world. name: Funeral Jewellery with Animal Hair - Memorial Decoration for Animal Friends made of Epoxy Resin - A Keepsake of the Beloved Pet - Personalized
description: Dear animal lovers,are you looking for a memory of your deceased companion?I make you a commemorative jewelry made of hair, ash or even teeth in epoxy resin.So you can always have your darling close to you beyond death.I've had it myself several times. I will never forget my Smilla. But now I will take the step; I will make myself a pendant from her ashes.I lost my father at the beginning of the year. The supervisor gave me a small capsule with a few hairs from my father. At first I found the idea strange, but now it gives me a reassuring feeling to always have it with me. Something tangible to underline the memories.Recently the dog died of good friends and the family asked me to make this pendant out of hair in the pictures. The daughter, 9 years old, had never been without the dog and it was terrible for her. She saw the trailer and was reassured to keep some of her "sister" and carry it with her.I also like to implement other forms and ideas, just write me a message.The heart in the pictures is about 3.5 cm wide and 3 cm high. Colors are also possible.I just need your concrete ideas and a few hairs, ashes or the like.I wish you much strength in this difficult time, your AnnaFlower Child

description: Kind taucht nach Muschel, Anh√§nger, Gie√üharz, 925 Sterling SilberDie kleinen Mini Muscheln sind echt und ich habe sie selber aus dem Rhein (Fluss) gesammelt.Im Harz sind Glitzerpartikel, die" Algen" sind aus echtem Moos.( Da die Farbe nur bedingt lichtecht ist habe ich den Preis von urspr√ºnglich 115,-Euro auf 75,- Euro gesenkt. Cotton ribbon any length at no extra charge.Please specify the desired length when ordering!Shipping as an insured registered letter "worldwide".If you have any questions or wishes, please feel free to contact me.  :)(If a chain is chosen, I will attach a smaller eyelet to the trailer because it is visually more beautiful and lies better!)

name: Sun Sign, (Divine/God Sign) Pendant, 585 Gold/ 925 Sterling Silver, with Chain, REAL Handmade
description: Sun pendant, 925 sterling silver, with 585 gold(Made to order!)I thought for such a trailer is slow time and a nice alternative to other characters....I had hoped it would be a little easier to implement, but it has become quite cumbersome.Since it is handmade, the trailer is not industrially perfect round.Here is some more information about this sign:Sun sign is the symbol of the divine and soul power. From the center, the divine power radiates to the outside.The symbol stands for the sun, Sunday and gold. It is also considered a powerful reinforcement sign, so that positive energies are amplified in all directions.Since the circle has neither beginning nor end, it also stands for infinity.The sun sign reflects the law of reflection and self-knowledge.Trust in yourself and the Divine independent of the outside.Recognition of one's own light and this from the inside (golden circle/point) to radiate /light outwards.It stands for God, the cosmic consciousness and enlightenment.Astrology= for the SunSun sign stands for the number 1Manufacturing process in brief:-Silver plate sawn out, polished and drilled in center hole-pre-polished and eyelet adapted and firmly soldered, polished-with cutter elaborately milled beams, then still with Diamantier file after machined- Self-made 585 gold wire guided through hole-from both sides gold wire with hammer pinned/ flat hammeredMeans the gold is not soldered on the surface,but passes through the silver plate, is forged, i.e. that in this case there is also more gold in the trailer than seen from the front!!!!Small trailer but a lot of work.The pendant comes in jewelry box with certificate!The chain length is included up to 50 cm.Please contact me BEFORE THE BUY if a longer chain is desired, as I have to charge a small extra charge from this length.Shipping takes place as INSURED EInletter worldwide!!!Made with heart! If you have any questions or wishes, please feel free to contact me. :)Dimensions:approx. 1.4 cm

description: Rose Quartz Gemstone and Healing Stone BraceletSymbolic effect:The delicate pink ish-red colour symbolizes the still young rose bud, which is just about to unfold. For this reason, rose quartz can be recommended for all life situations in which a change or new beginning takes place:Rose Quartz Raw StoneRose Quartz Raw Stonee.g. at birth, puberty, pregnancy, career change, menopause, divorce, euthanasia. With "gentle determination" the rose quartz helps to unfold itself and to realize its true needs.He stands for unconditional love, which is without judging. This includes being able to accept oneself and so the rose quartz can help lonely people to find in themselves the comfort and security that they have been denied in the outside. Rose quartz promotes empathy, which has a beneficial effect, especially in divorces or frequent disputes. Mistrust, fear, hatred and resentment dissolve and enable forgiveness. It makes it easier to accept others and themselves as they are and thus fosters a friendly atmosphere that is characterized by mutual respect. For this purpose, it is best to place a larger rose quartz chunk in the living/dining area or at the workplace. It should also not be missing in any children's room or living room of the elderly! Under the bed, it can help you get a better night's sleep.Just as the rose is the classic flower of love, rose quartz is the stone for all problems in the field of feelings, whether it is self-reproach or lack of respect for others or the environment. To be able to give love, I must first discard the (unconscious) conviction "I am not worth being loved" and begin to love myself. Only then can my love be visible in the outside.Physical effect:Radiaesthetic reviews showed that rose quartz positively affects relatively many frequencies. In particular, its effect in the area of the nervous system and in problems with the heart and blood circulation could be confirmed, probably due to the manganese content. It can be used well after a "mini-nerve collapse" because it supports strengthening and regeneration of nerves and also on the centers of healing, charity and responsibility.It also has frequencies in the area of digestion (feeling full, liver), acts on the skin (nails, warts, adipose tissue), the bone structure and the genital organs.The bracelet is with an elastic stretch band.
